{
  "stem": "10644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where I could meet the leftist leaders over the Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, please, Grinburg is in my apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They knew already everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They said-- they said, please be patient.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We will take him away when at the darkness.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And really, when it became dark, they came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They picked him up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they took him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it was, nevertheless-- I put my whole-- my whole career into danger.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If the Pole-- Poles followed him correctly and found him, I would be-- and I was keeping him-- I would be responsible.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that this people didn't forget.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they knew about this, when I didn't forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- that was all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- hold on, approximately 19-- 20-- 20-- 8-- '29.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and that is what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now it is 1939-- 10 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's the-- you cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that he was sent to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't want, you know, to appear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would be arrested, arrested, to go for four or five years into prison.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, he-- they sent him to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happened to him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But these men who managed all these things with him, who knew that I am keeping in my apartment was this same man, you know-- now in the administration.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So from one side, I was for him a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from the other side, I am the man who helped his, his, his-- and he just didn't make any, any, any, any, any noise, we'll say so.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'39--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--after this, oh, I was prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans were-- again.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
